          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Water Technology Acceleration Act</strong></p> <p>This bill provides support for developing and deploying&nbsp;emerging or innovative water technology, including by requiring the Environmental Protection Agency to carry out a grant program for accelerating the development of emerging or innovative water technologies that address pressing water challenges.</p>]]></text>
